data.description: This wonderful home is cozy, solidly built with 3 bd, 2 full bath home with generous master suite, and an excellent floor plan and open feeling. New exterior sealed paint, includes dryer and new washer included, new storm door, new wood stove chimney, roof upgrade around chimney, new gutters, new bathroom vanity, new interior paint. Large, beautiful yard with fully rebuilt terraced front yard wall. Flowers, trees (Quaking Aspen for shade), lawn, gravel, water fountain. New gravel in portion of back yard with heavy landscape fabric beneath. Peach tree, blackberry bush, and strawberries. An amazing oasis all enclosed with privacy fencing! Nice back patio area could readily be converted into an outdoor kitchen. This Lovely home has it all!!! Close to Sahalee Park, Saturday Market, Performing Arts Center, Aquatic Center, Walking Trails, and only ten minutes to Lake Billy Chinook and/or Lake Simtustus. Small town living! Must see!
